28:33.407 --> 28:36.453
<i>♪ The sun is shining ♪</i>

28:36.584 --> 28:40.936
<i>♪ And so the right thing ♪</i>

28:41.067 --> 28:46.420
<i>♪ To do is make it
shine for you ♪</i>

28:48.683 --> 28:53.949
<i>♪ A heart full of joy
and gladness ♪</i>

28:54.080 --> 28:59.259
<i>♪ Will always banish
sadness and strife ♪</i>

28:59.389 --> 29:05.526
<i>♪ So always look
