29:05.656 --> 29:08.529
<i>♪ And try to find ♪</i>

29:08.659 --> 29:11.837
<i>♪ The sunny side of life ♪</i>

29:11.967 --> 29:15.144
<i>♪ Always look for ♪</i>

29:15.275 --> 29:19.496
<i>♪ The silver lining ♪</i>

