<i>♪ Somebody loves me ♪</i>

44:37.805 --> 44:39.851
<i>♪ I wonder who ♪</i>

44:41.374 --> 44:45.595
<i>♪ I wonder who can she be ♪</i>

44:49.077 --> 44:52.124
<i>♪ Somebody needs me ♪</i>

44:53.691 --> 44:55.954
<i>♪ I wish I knew ♪</i>

44:57.346 --> 44:59.305
<i>♪ Who can she be ♪</i>

44:59.435 --> 45:01.829
<i>♪ Worries me ♪</i>

45:03.396 --> 45:06.965
<i>♪ To every girl who passes by ♪</i>

45:07.095 --> 45:08.183
<i>♪ I shout ♪</i>

45:08.314 --> 45:12.100
<i>♪ Hey, maybe ♪</i>

